License-file:        LICENSE
Author:              Joachim Breitner, Dennis Felsing
Maintainer:          Joachim Breitner <mail@joachim-breitner.de>
Copyright:           2012 Joachim Breitner
Category:            Debug, GHC
Build-type:          Custom
Cabal-version:       >=1.14
Extra-source-files:  Demo.hs

